{"tid":1880107,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Terezin 集中營 我見到嘅會唔會只係香港未來嘅縮影？","createTime":"2020-02-14T15:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T19:30:30.000Z","uid":199056,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3c17019a7e47feb53290d9e0c000e0b3deb0242c","tid":1880107,"uid":199056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"捷克比人嘅第一印象，大多數人諗到嘅應該都係「千塔之城」布拉格嘅文藝氣息，又或者係中世紀小鎮嘅美麗風光，好少人會將這個國家連繫到「悲傷」二字。然而，喺距離布拉格以北兩小時車程嘅地方，有一個刻印住中歐傷痕纍纍歷史喺城市，佢個名叫特雷辛 (Terezin)。<br />\n<br />\n講到二戰時期的集中營，大家第一時間可能會諗到位於波蘭、惡名昭彰嘅奧斯威辛集中營 (Auschwitz-Birkenau Concentration Camp)，集中營入面嘅勞動生活、以及令人聞風喪膽嘅毒氣室，成為左唔少人對納粹德國和二戰嘅第一印象，但係除左伊個屠殺左110萬無辜平民嘅滅絕營外，納粹德國喺二戰期間喺佢嘅佔領地興建左幾十個集中營同滅絕營，而當中Terezin集中營一定係特別的一個。<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，去圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFQ37gJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFQ37gJ.png&h=14b5b0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1JQNgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1JQNgO.png&h=9ba2bf7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Hq7Pu9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Hq7Pu9.png&h=c7c40f59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPqS0BU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPqS0BU.png&h=8d2bfb21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8AU4RJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8AU4RJG.png&h=39d9aff0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfpwwJN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfpwwJN.png&h=d03db756&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SO1OyXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSO1OyXc.png&h=be3a6b38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67cb8ea7ea74413df94c6a8db28972133fc20547","tid":1880107,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"推 等睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2699f6004d4c79a354107d9121b2c98b55b2caa","tid":1880107,"uid":302360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"留名 本身plan左月底去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee35bd28850d72ec4a5f3b730ab63b93a3320a32","tid":1880107,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da1dc7bb771a1599bb841e9500bf363055ac085","tid":1880107,"uid":199056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">二戰前的Terezin</span></ins><br />\nTerezin 喺十八世紀嗰陣係奧匈帝國建立嘅一個軍事防守要塞，後來到十九世紀為捷克斯洛伐克用作監獄。1938年，西方列強喺慕尼黑協定中將屬於捷克斯洛伐克的Sudetenland 地區 (捷克斯洛伐克境內嘅德語區) 割讓比納粹德國，以換取其不再侵略其他國家嘅領土。但歷史話比我地聽，相信納粹德國唔會有好結果 &mdash; 德軍喺一年後全面侵略捷克斯洛伐克，並將其國土納入版圖。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>Terezin 的規模</ins></span><br />\n喺二次世界大戰期間，納粹德國希望將來自世界各地嘅猶太人運至波蘭奧斯威辛集中營，因此Terezin 要塞又被納粹德軍改造為中轉營，成為僅次於波蘭奧斯威辛嘅世界第二大集中營，一開始德軍主要將佢作為運送捷克境內猶太人嘅主要中轉站，但鍳於其規模，Terezin 集中營亦逐漸接收來自世界各地嘅猶太人，並發展成猶太人隔離區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7pN6x6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7pN6x6n.jpg&h=45080d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTerezin 集中營共曾接收超過 140,000 人，當中約 33,000人於Terezin 因營養不良及疾病離世，超過 88,000人喺逗留數個月至數年之後被運送至其他滅絕營，喺蘇聯紅軍於1945年解放Terezin 之後，估計於集中營中的生還者只有約 19,000 人。五年間，數以萬計嘅人因惡劣嘅生活環境致死，而伊個僅僅只係一個中轉營嘅死亡數字，實際數字更令人側目，人類究竟要有幾殘忍才能漫不經心咁將一個族群全面滅絕？唔通自命高人一等就能夠掌握其他人嘅命運？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>Terezin集中營的特別之處</ins></span><br />\n二戰期間，納粹德國建立左幾十個唔同種類嘅集中營，當中包含勞動營、中轉營以及最令人聞風喪膽嘅滅絕營。Terezin 集中營並唔係滅絕營，只是一個中轉站以及猶太隔離區。佢冇毒氣室，表面上佢只是一個設施齊全嘅小社區，幼稚園、學校、超級市場等公共設施應有盡有。納粹德國對外標榜Terezin 係一個比猶太人過退休生活的温泉小鎮，並鼓勵猶太人簽訂租約、比租金，藉此吸引佢地前往Terezin。然而，裡面嘅環境真係好似佢表述的一般美好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n殘酷嘅現實是當猶太人抵達Terezin 之後，先發覺一切都只係假象。Terezin 嘅生活環境惡劣，猶太人需要進行無止境嘅勞動工作。温泉小鎮、退休生活等都都只係美麗嘅謊言，甚至當初簽嘅的租約也是偽造出嚟嘅。當國際紅十字會嘅志願人員前去評估市民嘅生活狀況，納粹政權更將Terezin 營造成歌舞昇平咁樣，終使佢地比納粹政權粉飾太平的假象蒙騙。伊個城市，正正就是咁虛假而真實嘅存在。<br />\n<br />\nTerezin 並唔係全個城市都是集中營，城市的大多數地方都係猶太隔離區(Ghetto)，只有前身為監獄嘅Small Fortress 係被稱為集中營嘅部分。所謂猶太隔離區，就是納粹德國為左方便管理猶太人而設立嘅區域，猶太人需要喺隔離區進行勞動工作。事實上，猶太隔離區只係納粹政府為左美化Terezin 而取嘅名字，現實中喺Terezin嘅生活與在集中營中無分別。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯威辛集中營（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP8tMt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP8tMt5.jpg&h=8291952f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSmall Fortress 嘅入口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WR48Muv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWR48Muv.png&h=3dfa6a1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"789a768a85f4b833b39aeb0390a74032c746d262","tid":1880107,"uid":199056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思啊大家因為我本身有寫blog 所以原本篇文寫左書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有啲書面語口語夾雜大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e1fa501a45467acd682fd7306f94e1ec964f73","tid":1880107,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"太長，<br />\n一般網絡forum俾太多資料無咩人睇<br />\n一幅圖一個caption加多句個人feeling多人睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90ef59c1a552546b87ea8400fbfeaba1fa54198","tid":1880107,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5f2299679ba21e31c0d26f573377841dab8db9","tid":1880107,"uid":135164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鍾意睇呢類題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb068a6ab52f249429352ca87e83373ddf68a90","tid":1880107,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1A6CFKhGEc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl1A6CFKhGEc&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNn%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=5e64ce92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1A6CFKhGEc</a>"},{"pid":"1100b9c4f6c295281f164944a7cda4fc724bbbde","tid":1880107,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=muIK215n3AU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmuIK215n3AU&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNn%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=bf376383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=muIK215n3AU</a>"},{"pid":"4615d9e40bd258849886d59aa2893fdd7a269c8c","tid":1880107,"uid":199056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"第一站：舊猶太墳場 (Jewish Cemetery) 和火葬場 (Crematorium)<br />\n<br />\n啱啱落車就見到一塊大石，呢塊石係用嚟紀念喺二戰中因納粹德國嘅種族屠殺而亡的猶太人，同埋紀念納粹集中營得以解放的一刻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWMWiDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWMWiDv.png&h=6f5ef7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一片樹林如果放喺其他地方可能係美麗嘅景色，但喺呢到淨係顯得更加寧靜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qz1GuNP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqz1GuNP.png&h=fc01e7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n穿過樹林就會見到舊猶太墳場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrPpsz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrPpsz3.png&h=9caade93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊猶太墳場喺二戰前已經用嚟做安葬死去嘅猶太人。二戰期間，由於喺猶太隔離區入面逝世嘅猶太人太多，只好再喺集中營外另僻一片空地安葬猶太人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HKXNAw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HKXNAw.png&h=f03a6643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n猶太墳場隔離就係火葬場，宜家被改建成一個小型嘅紀念館。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gXqWug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gXqWug.png&h=abb19d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紀念館入面展示左當年納粹嘅一啲檔案，以及簡述Terezin 喺成為集中營後至今嘅變遷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLKT5nV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLKT5nV.png&h=515a9577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7032egH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7032egH.png&h=074453b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紀念館入面都保留左一個當年用作火化嘅機器，喺冬天嗰陣佢亦可用作渦輪取暖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTSykXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTSykXr.png&h=cb0d3cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後人喺呢部機器上以花圈致意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YgXKsCF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgXKsCF.png&h=08732c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢部機器，背後到底承載住幾多人嘅傷痛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二站：死亡列車路軌<br />\n作為中轉營，Terezin 當時設有火車前往其他集中營，而連接Terezin 和波蘭奧斯威辛集中營嘅火車亦被稱為「死亡列車」。<br />\n<br />\n猶太人乘搭火車進入Terezin 嘅情景。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P91uRv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P91uRv.png&h=b081cdaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n登上「死亡列車」同有去無回無分別，每一班車乘載1000人前往奧斯威辛，往往到最後只有幾個人可以生還。<br />\n<br />\n宜家火車站已經不復存在，淨返嘅就只有當初由集中營嘅囚犯辛苦建成嘅火車路軌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mb95b4Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMb95b4Y.png&h=8cd412cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火車路軌側邊係一個存在骨灰嘅地方，現在供人紀念同祭拜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hqPDLa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hqPDLa.png&h=ba4e9909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諷刺嘅係，列車上嘅乘客從來唔知道自己下一站要前往何處，佢地只認為自己需要前往另一個集中營進行勞動，或者佢地仍然相信勞動能為自己帶嚟自由，但現實是佢地只是供納粹德國用作勞動嘅工具，沒有用途嘅時候只會被送到滅絕營處死。<br />\n<br />\n自由，對當時的猶太人嚟講只係遙遠而不設實際嘅想像。"},{"pid":"35743e69d527b60cff5f9c1905dbb5cbd2a32fb2","tid":1880107,"uid":199056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8e1fa501a45467acd682fd7306f94e1ec964f73","tid":1880107,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"太長，<br />\n一般網絡forum俾太多資料無咩人睇<br />\n一幅圖一個caption加多句個人feeling多人睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係第一篇想大家知多啲背景先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1686f21285b3a47914782e998c3c21dc6c7f8e3e","tid":1880107,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n其實都唔洗講到二戰咁遠<br />\n依家已經有新疆呢個活生生嘅例子喺正我地隔離<br />\n而呢種1984式嘅集中營比起納粹德國嘅更加恐怖"},{"pid":"20dc8f38632a94d76137a91042931e56f0c9355d","tid":1880107,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eda579a1ce438c047aca4f943a3fa9884287dba","tid":1880107,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95044d0d11a22f6594f1be606c51922f10fdcb4","tid":1880107,"uid":334812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n自己覺得冬天去的集中營的衝擊感仲大<br />\n然後 睇親所有去集中營的遊記 連自己去個陣都幾乎實係陰天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6105a60541cde180391797bbef224652eeb92169","tid":1880107,"uid":23930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"上次預得唔夠多時間，睇得有啲急，但真係好值得去"},{"pid":"0e13cd16306e04bd02702107865b8dfee2b35e1f","tid":1880107,"uid":276694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:30:30.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}